{"tid":1510504,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"團聚煲底，不必驚怕，口罩通通脫下，慶賀新生這地方，與你相擁：【反送中原創】「孵化」","createTime":"2019-08-27T08:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:45:25.000Z","uid":300718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85a34caf840ada38982c8e89ef2cfeab6eb0aa02","tid":1510504,"uid":300718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XoG34GYf78o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXoG34GYf78o&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=fe6a97cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XoG34GYf78o</a><br />\n曲、詞：任姓男子<br />\n<br />\n曾共你 <span style=\"color: blue;\">二百幾萬</span>人 一同上街<br />\n仍沒法 逆轉當權的<span style=\"color: blue;\">曲 解</span><br />\n拿著<span style=\"color: blue;\">傘</span> 用抗爭換來 槍林雨彈<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">燃</span>盡我 未怕迫害磨滅<br />\n<br />\n未分化 <span style=\"color: blue;\">不篤灰 核彈</span>也 <span style=\"color: blue;\">不割席</span><br />\n各本起 <span style=\"color: blue;\">良心</span>去 <span style=\"color: blue;\">爬山</span><br />\n<br />\n讓這<span style=\"color: blue;\">雞蛋</span> 撞向了<span style=\"color: blue;\">石牆</span><br />\n讓這聲音 永不退讓<br />\n容讓我作 <span style=\"color: blue;\">犧牲</span>的羔羊<br />\n無懼惡政 掀開<span style=\"color: blue;\">真相</span><br />\n<br />\n望這<span style=\"color: blue;\">子彈</span> 射向我面龐<br />\n就算畫面 瞬間暗淡<br />\n憑著你我 心中的<span style=\"color: blue;\">光芒</span><br />\n凝望遠處再次奔往<br />\n<br />\n面對威迫 未抹去<span style=\"color: blue;\">善良</span><br />\n讓那虛假 瞬間畏懼<br />\n然後一天 <span style=\"color: blue;\">擊倒這高牆</span><br />\n重遇你我 這天終於<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">團聚煲底</span> 不必驚怕 <span style=\"color: blue;\">口罩通通脫下</span><br />\n慶賀新生這地方<br />\n與你<span style=\"color: blue;\">相擁</span><br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n呢首歌我由雨傘作好左Chorus，到呢個禮拜先拎番出黎作埋佢，實在愧對大家。<br />\n盡左力作，希望大家有共鳴，能夠鼓勵到每一位手足，堅持落去！<br />\n如果睇得動漫多，你會知道，<span style=\"color: red;\">歌既力量可以勁過核彈</span>！所謂各自爬山，希望呢條戰線有得推。<br />\n非常歡迎大家拎首歌重編/重唱/重填 (話哂呢個只係盡力粗製版..)，Chord可以問我拎，只要幫到我地贏到，點都得！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d43d5226ed5d8f1001a97374eadad133352451","tid":1510504,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:10:59.000Z","msg":"快過呂麗<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"06c6fd6b631e31edd08ba6d3e02531c3672e22f3","tid":1510504,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:11:23.000Z","msg":"呂麗乳搖 慢過我"},{"pid":"9d7b5089bc431dc2690cbd5902083ad85917deef","tid":1510504,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=69a8b563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=00a8e0cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=f7a80d0a\" data-auto